      label="Dragonfly SDK"
      version="2.0.0.qualifier"
      provider-name="Bug Labs, Inc."
      plugin="com.buglabs.dragonfly.ui">

   <description>
      The BUG SDK, called Dragonfly, is how you connect your computer with your BUG. In the SDK you can modify the properties of your BUG, configure modules, and create new BUG applications. Finally, Dragonfly interacts with BUGnet so you can upload and download applications to and from your computer or your BUG.
